description:
Avengers: The Children's Crusade

▸ With his reality-altering powers spiraling out of his control, Young Avenger Wiccan sets out to find the one person who may be able to help him – the Scarlet Witch, the woman purported to be his mother. But as Billy Kaplan embarks on this quest, he finds himself pitted against the Avengers, X-Men…and even his teammates. Industry great Allan Heinberg delivers this super-powered coming-of-age tale!
